{"tid":559682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網上聲稱籌錢助死傷者　25歲女涉呃人被捕","createTime":"2018-02-13T11:26:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-13T13:41:02.000Z","uid":15440,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"d4df7f9a2beff2510acedf3088feb76729c59f7d","tid":559682,"uid":15440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T11:26:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1206771/xlarge/7935a6ae768ad224b29fa81259e212a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1206771%2Fxlarge%2F7935a6ae768ad224b29fa81259e212a7.jpg&h=f4724bd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大埔公路九巴翻側釀19死66傷車禍，繼30歲男司機落網後，警方再拘捕一名25歲女子，涉嫌於網上自稱為死傷者親屬，並發布銀行號碼呼籲市民捐款。警方今日拘捕一名25歲女子，涉嫌有犯罪或不誠實意圖取用電腦。案件涉及有人早前於社交平台上，自稱其家人為大埔公路車禍的死者家屬，聲稱希望呼籲市民捐款予其銀行戶口，「希望大家可以略盡綿力，讓我姑奶家人會好過一點及重新振作起來」，又指會將善款全數交及遺孀。帖文於網上被網民狠批「發死人財」，直指其為「呃錢」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/article/159036\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F159036&d=jsqmDAceei3L%2FEVJ%2FIjPbk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=7c0a46aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/article/159036</a>"},{"pid":"a311dd62ba7b624dbe4996a5b1cc7fe87d49d1da","tid":559682,"uid":20227,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T11:28:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8a84da0131b855505b9d069c9a39e14e85a2cf0f","tid":559682,"uid":25822,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T11:33:55.000Z","msg":"抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f6a940eff546de623179885dceb54ffc11e666d","tid":559682,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T11:35:55.000Z","msg":"肥婆？"},{"pid":"1235a6a820711ff935ebafd304a1be02ed12cf1e","tid":559682,"uid":62487,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score"